Libraries

Frameworks: Laravel, Bootstrap, Font Awesome, tinyMCE

Languages: PHP, HTML, JQuery

Databases: SQLite3 during development, MySQL during production

Server: apache as http, nginx as application

Caching: file during development, Redis during production

Mail: Mailgun API

SMS: Hulksms API